about.summary: Python file chooser widget for use in Jupyter/IPython in conjunction with ipywidgets

name: ipyfilechooser
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "ipyfilechooser" %}
{% set version = "0.3.4" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 705a8a0d36b87414a72ab81a0327d3201a85e8f68ba1c70aa4f0250e1192a0db

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - ipywidgets
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - ipyfilechooser

about:
  home: "https://github.com/crahan/ipyfilechooser"
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  # https://github.com/crahan/ipyfilechooser/issues/20
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "Python file chooser widget for use in Jupyter/IPython in conjunction with ipywidgets"
  dev_url: https://github.com/crahan/ipyfilechooser

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - crahan
